				\begin{document}$$ {\mathbf{v}} = {\mathbf{0}}\quad {\text{for the wall }} $$\end{document}</tex-math><graphic xlink:href="449_2010_469_Article_Equ18.gif" position="anchor"/></alternatives></disp-formula><disp-formula id="Equ19"><label>15b</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M19">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
