				\begin{document}$$ {\mathbf{v}} = [0,0,v_{0} ]\quad {\text{at the inlet }} $$\end{document}</tex-math><graphic xlink:href="449_2010_469_Article_Equ19.gif" position="anchor"/></alternatives></disp-formula><disp-formula id="Equ20"><label>15c</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M20">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
